query: INSERT INTO labels (subject, rkey, value, reason, actor, expires_at, created_at, ingested_at) VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, extract(epoch from now())::BIGINT) ON CONFLICT(subject, rkey) DO UPDATE SET reason = excluded.reason, actor = excluded.actor, value = excluded.value, expires_at = excluded.expires_at
